<section id="service-areas" class="service-areas-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="title" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800">
            Serving Central Kentucky
        </div>
        <div class="cities-grid">
            <div class="city-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100" data-aos-anchor-placement="top-bottom">
                <div class="city-header">
                    <div class="city-icon">
                        <i class="bi bi-geo-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Richmond, KY</h3>
                </div>
                <p>Our home base in Madison County. Complete garage door services including emergency repairs, installations, and maintenance for residential and commercial properties.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="city-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="150" data-aos-anchor-placement="top-bottom">
                <div class="city-header">
                    <div class="city-icon">
                        <i class="bi bi-geo-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Lexington, KY</h3>
                </div>
                <p>Expert garage door repair and installation in Fayette County. Serving the Bluegrass region with reliable, professional service you can trust.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="city-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200" data-aos-anchor-placement="top-bottom">
                <div class="city-header">
                    <div class="city-icon">
                        <i class="bi bi-geo-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Surrounding Areas</h3>
                </div>
                <p>We also serve Berea, Nicholasville, Lancaster, Danville, and other communities throughout Madison, Jessamine, Garrard, and Boyle counties.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .service-areas-section {
        background-color: var(--background-50);
        padding: 4rem 1rem;
    }

    .title {
        font-size: 3.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--text-800);
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        text-align: left;
        line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .cities-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 2.5rem;
        align-items: stretch;
    }

    .city-item {
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: left;
        background-color: white;
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-600);
        padding: 2rem;
        -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
        touch-action: manipulation;
        backface-visibility: hidden;
        -webkit-backface-visibility: hidden;
    }

    .city-item:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    .city-header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .city-icon {
        width: 3rem;
        height: 3rem;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        color: white;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-600), var(--primary-750));
    }

    .city-item h3 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--text-800);
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 1.3;
        flex: 1;
    }

    .city-item p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: var(--text-600);
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 1.5;
        flex: 1;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .cities-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
            align-items: start;
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .city-item {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .city-item:hover {
            transform: none;
            box-shadow: none;
        }

        .city-header {
            flex-direction: column;
            text-align: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
        }

        .city-item h3 {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .city-item p {
            text-align: center;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) and (min-width: 769px) {
        .cities-grid {
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 3rem;
        }
    }
</style>